text: Imane Anys ( (Arabic pronunciation: ); born 14 May 1996), better known by her online name, Pokimane, is a Moroccan-Canadian internet personality. She is a Twitch streamer and YouTuber. Anys is best known for her live streams on Twitch, where she is best known for playing League of Legends and Fortnite. She is a member of OfflineTV. ==Early Life== Anys was born on May 14, 1996 in Morocco. Anys and her parents later moved to Canada. Anys made her YouTube channel in 2014. ==Career== Anys started Twitch in 2013. She likes video games in Twitch and YouTube including Fortnite, League of Legends, Valorant, Minecraft, and Among Us. In 2024 she left Twitch. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Moroccan entertainers Category:Canadian YouTubers Category:Twitch (service) streamers
